orestes.bloomfilter.redis

Class CBloomFilterRedisBits<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • orestes.bloomfilter.BloomFilter<T>
      • orestes.bloomfilter.CBloomFilter<T>
        • orestes.bloomfilter.redis.CBloomFilterRedisBits<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T -
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable

    public class CBloomFilterRedisBits<T>
extends CBloomFilter<T>
    This Redis-backed bloomfilter stores the counting bits in a bit array and uses Lua scripting (available in Redis 2.6 and above) to access it efficiently.
